---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Machina"
  description="Machina is the AI briefing for people who build and run things. We cover AI through the lens of business impact — tools, case studies, and signal."
>
  <article style="max-width:640px;">
    <h1 style="font-size:2rem; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:-0.03em; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">About Machina</h1>

    <p style="color:var(--brand-muted); font-size:1.05rem; margin-bottom:2rem;">
      <em>The AI briefing for people who build and run things.</em>
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; margin:2rem 0 0.75rem;">What we are</h2>
    <p>Machina is not another AI news roundup. There are plenty of those. We cover AI through the lens of
    <strong>business impact</strong> — which tools actually move revenue, how real companies are deploying
    AI to build competitive moats, and what the week's noise means for operators and decision-makers.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; margin:2rem 0 0.75rem;">Who we're for</h2>
    <p>Founders, operators, product leaders, and anyone building or running a business in the age of AI.
    If you make decisions that touch technology — and increasingly, that's everyone — Machina is built for you.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; margin:2rem 0 0.75rem;">What you get</h2>
    <ul style="padding-left:1.25rem; color:var(--brand-muted);">
      <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;"><strong style="color:var(--brand-text)">Weekly briefings</strong> — the AI news that actually matters, filtered for business impact</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;"><strong style="color:var(--brand-text)">Tool teardowns</strong> — honest deep dives on tools gaining traction with real operators</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;"><strong style="color:var(--brand-text)">Case studies</strong> — real deployments with real numbers, not press releases</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:700; margin:2rem 0 0.75rem;">Editorial principles</h2>
    <p>We don't take money for coverage. Every tool we review, every case study we feature, is independently
    selected. Sponsors are clearly labeled. Our job is to be the most trusted signal in a noisy space —
    we protect that rigorously.</p>

    <div class="subscribe-bar" style="margin-top:3rem;">
      <h2>Join the briefing.</h2>
      <p>Free. No spam. Unsubscribe any time.</p>
      <div class="subscribe-form">
        <input type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" aria-label="Email address" />
        <button class="btn">Subscribe</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
